snippet.title: Tomb Raider Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Evercade VS. This is one of the first two Evercade releases to come in a Giga cart, which means there's enough space to fit in multiple CD games.

Games in this cart:
00:00 - Intro
00:23 - Tomb Raider
14:20 - Tomb Raider II
32:36 - Tomb Raider III

Tomb Raider, Tomb Raider II, Tomb Raider III (C) Crystal Dynamics
Originally developed by Core Design
